reviewText: I read your review about only getting one DVD.... But did not heed your warning. I ALSO ONLY RECEIVED ONE DVD when the description said 5 DVDS....

It said:
This set has the following 5 DVDs of Hillsong KIDS Titles:
01. SUPERNATURAL
02. JESUS SUPER HERO
03. SUPER STRONG GOD
04. FOLLOW YOU
05. TELL THE WORLD

But I only received a single DVD with title 'Follow You'. Where is the other 4 DVDs?
